Description:
lstat() function: return information about a file or symbolic link.

Files:
lib/lstat.c
m4/lstat.m4

Depends-on:
sys_stat
largefile
dosname         [test $REPLACE_LSTAT = 1]
stat            [test $REPLACE_LSTAT = 1]

configure.ac:
gl_FUNC_LSTAT
if test $REPLACE_LSTAT = 1; then
  AC_LIBOBJ([lstat])
  gl_PREREQ_LSTAT
fi
gl_SYS_STAT_MODULE_INDICATOR([lstat])

